products.content:
We are Shopify design and development experts.
Our team helps brands with the following: custom store and theme functionality, custom theme sections and pages, smaller page fixes and layout changes, complex implementations, store setups and migrations, theme updates, custom page and section design mockups, banner and ad creatives, in depth UI/UX and functionality audits and so much more. Check out our project ideas section for inspiration.

products.title: What type of projects do you handle?

products.content:
With our standard "fast turnaround", we'd be able to deliver on a 5-hour project, within 5 business days – counting from the moment your project payment was confirmed – whereas agencies and freelancers will usually put your project on a longer queue.

Our "express turnaround" roughly equates to a 2x faster delivery. For instance, the same 5-hour project could be delivered within 2-3 business days, depending on our work backlog. Even though we can be busier at times, if you upgrade to "express turnaround" your project will always be given highest priority.

products.content:
Moving between platforms can be a pretty daunting task. But it doesn’t have to be. Most of our Shopify Plus projects involve migrating brands from Magento, CommerceCloud alongside other e-commerce platforms.

So, if we’re handling your brand’s replatforming project, know you’ll be in safe hands. By this, we mean your data will be transferred seamlessly. Your integrations, connected flawlessly. And all that traffic kept safe and sound.

products.title: Why migrate to Shopify?

products.content: We help you with all project management. We assign a project manager to your account as your primary contact. This person will coordinate the necessary team members to execute on design and development projects, they will report progress to you on a schedule you both agree on, get your feedback and ultimately lead the project forward. Your project manager is also there to make strategic suggestions based on your specific business goals. Our goal is to take ownership and accountability of the process from start to finish. Let us worry, so you don’t have to.
